#originalTopic=Gun_Control_Should_Be_Made_Stricter_In_America
 Let the criminals get firearms. Let their victims get firearms too. Then see who wins. There are more good people than there are criminals. The laws restricting firearm ownership or the right to carry firearms around collectively constitute a criminals' charter. If everyone carried a gun around with them at all times, there would be hardly any crime.